ll defaults. Use this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to override products and whether it ignores the subscription status. Defaults to "},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An optional completion block that gets called when the paywall should dismiss. This defaults to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":" and the SDK"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"will call "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"presentationMode.wrappedValue.dismiss()"},{"type":"text","text":" by default. Otherwise you must perform the dismissal of the paywall."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"onRequestDismiss"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"A completion block containing a feature that you wish to paywall. Access to this block is remotely configurable via the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"https:\/\/superwall.com\/dashboard","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":". If the paywall is set to ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Non Gated"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":", this will be called when","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the paywall is dismissed or if the user is already paying. If the paywall is ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Gated"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":", this will be called only if the user is already paying","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"or if they begin paying. If no paywall is configured, this gets called immediately. This will not be called in the event of an error.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"feature"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This uses ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/superwall-ios.SuperwallKit\/documentation\/SuperwallKit\/Superwall\/getPaywall(forPla